rows.label: tev000711_MSG0010
rows.name:
Hot dang... Talk about a five-alarm
situation. Hard to keep up with all the
bailing out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0020
rows.name:
But that's neither here nor there.
We'll just have to plant our boots on
the ground and do what we do best.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0030
rows.name:
Not that I need to tell YOUâ€”I bet you're
all over it. You want a hand? 'Cause I got
two and they're itchin' for work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0060
rows.name: Music to my ears. Then let's move out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0090
rows.name:
You're the boss. Just don't put too much
on your own shoulders, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0100
rows.name:
We're facing the battle to end
all battles, right? Obviously it's
gotta be us that end it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0110
rows.name:
It's gonna be grueling as all get-out,
but with you and Elma on our side, I'm
confident things'll work out somehow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev000711_MSG0120
rows.name:
And my gut's rarely wrong about
these things. But still, let's both
stay safe out there.[ST:wait ]
